name: Day In Day Out (Fade Away)
description:
come inside to see the lies beneath it
city lights don't deceive me anymore
the sun will rise again you see it's just a phase
and time will fade

day in day out fade away
everything never stays the same
water over my head
wash away the shame
incinerate my dreams again

i followed the moon into the dark
she showed me all the way
i'm no more lost
when darkness fade away
the dawn will break the silence
screaming in our hearts the truth

day in day out fade away
everything never stays the same
water over my head
wash away the shame
incinerate my dreams again

original song by Lia Evol  (@lia.evol)
visuals by femboylavagirl (@g.r.i.e.f)
